type for playback all:
  waldo.py p pojectfoldername
           ^
type for single playback:
  waldo.py sp pojectfoldername channelfilename (songname)
           ^^
type for recording:
  waldo.py r pojectfoldername channelfilename servopin (songname)
           ^
abort recoding
  ctrl + c

type for detecting and saving usb port / baudrate for recording:
  waldo.py usb
           ^^^
type for channels infomation:
  waldo.py ls
           ^^
type fo copyright information:
  python waldo.py c
                  ^
